      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GameLoop does not emit sockets directly. It calls Trucoshi callbacks; Trucoshi emits waits, chat sounds, match updates, persists hand rows, and handles turn/disconnect timeouts.",
