      "originalText": "Trucoshi stores external IDs instead of cross-database FKs:\n- Match.ownerAccountId -> accounts.User.id\n- MatchPlayer.accountId -> accounts.User.id\n- MatchPlayer.payRequestId -> accounts.PayRequest.id\n- UserStats.accountId -> accounts.User.id",
